import { FormLabel, Select } from "@chakra-ui/react"

const Cour = () => {
    return (
        <>
            <FormLabel>クール</FormLabel>
            <Select >
                <option>1期（冬期）</option>
                <option>2期（春期）</option>
                <option>3期（夏期）</option>
                <option>4期（秋期）</option>
            </Select>
        </>
    )
}

export default Cour
